@startuml
title RWA Tokenized Compliance System - Production Admin Approval Flow

actor "Compliance Admin" as Admin
participant "Admin Dashboard" as AdminUI
participant "Compliance Service" as Compliance
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "KMS/Vault Signer" as Signer
participant "Identity Registry" as Registry

Admin -> AdminUI : Review KYC request
AdminUI -> Compliance : POST /api/admin request\nwith X-Admin-Token
Compliance -> DB : Persist decision and audit event
alt Approved
    Compliance -> Signer : Request addIdentity transaction
    Signer -> Registry : addIdentity(wallet, documentHash)
    Registry --> Compliance : Approval tx receipt
    Compliance -> DB : Store tx hash and approved status
else Rejected
    Compliance -> DB : Store rejection reason
end
Compliance --> AdminUI : Show final status and audit event
@enduml